## Reproducibility

All numerical experiments shown in the paper that involve:

- derivative accuracy comparisons
- forward model validation
- stability assessments

can be reproduced using the scripts in the `examples/` directory.

Numerical parameters (grid spacing, time step, domain size) are chosen consistently with the values reported in the manuscript.

